body_html:
Hi samikama,

I figured out the solution. The root cause that I can't get calibration successfully done is because calibration can't accept batch input. Now I changed to run session 1 image at a time in the calibration, and it indeed works.

Thanks for your reply. You convinced me on this.

body:
Hi samikama,

I figured out the solution. The root cause that I can't get calibration successfully done is because calibration can't accept batch input. Now I changed to run session 1 image at a time in the calibration, and it indeed works.

Thanks for your reply. You convinced me on this.
